name: Neophyte Prototype 001
description:
Neophyte, an ongoing ode to the computational beauty of nature.

Neophyte is a software based artwork and tool for generating plant life that I originally developed in 2011. Since then I've re-factored it across four programming languages and used it in nearly a dozen artworks. 

The latest of Neophyte is still under development, and this is an artifact from that development
